TITLE: SDL3 Custom Read Function
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the updated custom read function for SDL3, utilizing SDL_ReadIO. The function handles edge cases where size or nitems is zero and adjusts the return value to match the expected behavior of SDL2's SDL_RWread.
SOURCE: https://github.com/libsdl-org/sdlwiki/blob/main/SDL3/README/migration.md#_snippet_33

LANGUAGE: C
CODE:
```
size_t custom_read(void *ptr, size_t size, size_t nitems, SDL_IOStream *stream)
{
    if (size > 0 && nitems > 0) {
        return SDL_ReadIO(stream, ptr, size * nitems) / size;
    }
    return 0;
}
```

