TITLE: Install pkg-config .pc files for SDL (SDL2 renamed to SDL3)
DESCRIPTION: Installs the pkg-config `.pc` files for SDL3, SDL3_image, SDL3_mixer, SDL3_net and SDL3_ttf by creating files in the `pkgconfig` directory. This allows tools like `pkg-config` to find the correct compiler and linker flags for SDL3 libraries.  Note: The name in the file is kept as sdl2, but the libs and includes point to SDL3.
SOURCE: https://github.com/libsdl-org/sdlwiki/blob/main/SDL3/Android.md#_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
cat <<'EOF' > $NDK_STANDALONE/sysroot/usr/lib/pkgconfig/sdl2.pc
prefix=/usr/src/ndk-standalone-14-arm/sysroot/usr
exec_prefix=${prefix}
libdir=${exec_prefix}/lib
includedir=${prefix}/include
Name: sdl2
Description: Simple DirectMedia Layer is a cross-platform multimedia library designed to provide low level access to audio, keyboard, mouse, joystick, 3D hardware via OpenGL, and 2D video framebuffer.
Version: 2.0.5
Requires:
Conflicts:
Libs: -lSDL3
Cflags: -I${includedir}/SDL3   -D_REENTRANT
EOF
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
cat <<'EOF' > $NDK_STANDALONE/sysroot/usr/lib/pkgconfig/SDL3_image.pc
prefix=/usr/src/ndk-standalone-14-arm/sysroot/usr
exec_prefix=${prefix}
libdir=${exec_prefix}/lib
includedir=${prefix}/include
Name: SDL3_image
Description: image loading library for Simple DirectMedia Layer
Version: 2.0.1
Requires: sdl2 >= 2.0.0
Libs: -L${libdir} -lSDL3_image
Cflags: -I${includedir}/SDL3
EOF
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
cat <<'EOF' > $NDK_STANDALONE/sysroot/usr/lib/pkgconfig/SDL3_mixer.pc
prefix=/usr/src/ndk-standalone-14-arm/sysroot/usr
exec_prefix=${prefix}
libdir=${exec_prefix}/lib
includedir=${prefix}/include
Name: SDL3_mixer
Description: mixer library for Simple DirectMedia Layer
Version: 2.0.1
Requires: sdl2 >= 2.0.0
Libs: -L${libdir} -lSDL3_mixer
Cflags: -I${includedir}/SDL3
EOF
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
cat <<'EOF' > $NDK_STANDALONE/sysroot/usr/lib/pkgconfig/SDL3_net.pc
prefix=/usr/src/ndk-standalone-14-arm/sysroot/usr
exec_prefix=${prefix}
libdir=${exec_prefix}/lib
includedir=${prefix}/include
Name: SDL3_net
Description: net library for Simple DirectMedia Layer
Version: 2.0.1
Requires: sdl2 >= 2.0.0
Libs: -L${libdir} -lSDL3_net
Cflags: -I${includedir}/SDL3
EOF
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
cat <<'EOF' > $NDK_STANDALONE/sysroot/usr/lib/pkgconfig/SDL3_ttf.pc
prefix=/usr/src/ndk-standalone-14-arm/sysroot/usr
