TITLE: TTF_SubString Flags Macros
DESCRIPTION: These macros define specific flags that can be combined to describe the characteristics of a text substring when using `TTF_SubString` in SDL_ttf.  `TTF_SUBSTRING_DIRECTION_MASK` provides a mask for direction, while others identify the start/end of text or a specific line. These flags are used to determine substring flow direction and position within a text.
