TITLE: Install pkg-config for Android NDK
DESCRIPTION: Installs pkg-config into the standalone NDK sysroot. Downloads, extracts, configures, builds, and installs pkg-config. Creates a symbolic link for the Android-specific pkg-config binary in the toolchain's bin directory.  Also creates the directory for the .pc files.
