TITLE: Example Frame Rendering Callback for iOS with SDL in C++
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet provides an example of a frame rendering callback function, `ShowFrame`, which is used in conjunction with `SDL_iPhoneSetAnimationCallback` on iOS. The callback handles event processing, frame logic, and rendering.  An example of how to initialize SDL and the game center.
