TITLE: Define SDL_GPUStencilOp enum in C
DESCRIPTION: Defines the SDL_GPUStencilOp enum, which specifies the operation to perform on the stencil buffer. The available operations include keeping the current value, setting it to zero, replacing it with a reference value, incrementing and clamping, decrementing and clamping, inverting, incrementing and wrapping, and decrementing and wrapping.  This enum is used to configure stencil testing behavior in SDL_gpu.
