TITLE: Handling Background Events on Mobile in SDL3
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet illustrates how to use an event filter to catch SDL_EVENT_WILL_ENTER_BACKGROUND events on mobile platforms in SDL3. This allows immediate handling of critical events to prevent application termination by the OS.
