TITLE: SDL_GPUShaderCreateInfo Structure Definition in C
DESCRIPTION: Defines the SDL_GPUShaderCreateInfo structure, which holds the data needed to create a GPU shader. This includes the shader code, entry point, format, stage, and resource counts. It's available since SDL 3.2.0.
