TITLE: SDL_GPUSamplerCreateInfo Structure Definition in C
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the SDL_GPUSamplerCreateInfo structure, used to specify the parameters for creating a GPU sampler in SDL3. It includes members for filtering modes (min_filter, mag_filter), mipmap mode, addressing modes (address_mode_u, address_mode_v, address_mode_w), LOD bias, anisotropy, comparison operation, LOD clamping, and flags for enabling anisotropic filtering and comparison. It also includes a properties ID for extensions.
