LANGUAGE: C
CODE:
```
const SDL_AssertData *item = SDL_GetAssertionReport();
while (item) {
   printf("'%s', %s (%s:%d), triggered %u times, always ignore: %s.\n",
          item->condition, item->function, item->filename,
          item->linenum, item->trigger_count,
          item->always_ignore ? "yes" : "no");
   item = item->next;
}
```

