TITLE: SDL_GPURasterizerState Structure Definition in C
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the structure `SDL_GPURasterizerState` in C. It encapsulates various parameters controlling the rasterization stage of the graphics pipeline, including fill mode, cull mode, front face orientation, depth bias settings, and depth clipping/clamping behavior. This structure allows developers to configure how primitives are rendered and how depth values are handled. The structure is available since SDL 3.2.0.
